name: where they are?
description:
Original illustration 2160 x 3840 px

Where are they? where are those works that we left behind, that we burned? we can be conservative and think that they are simply in a virtual place locked with a key that no one has.
 But I prefer to believe that they are going to a different world than ours, some might call this place hell but it is simply a different place with different inhabitants than us. In this world these characters live, have fun and also fall in love without any kind of barrier.

Used technique: Vectorial illustration + edition
